Barchart,is,a,provider,of,futures,equity,and,foreign,exchange,market,data,The,getFinancialRatios,API,provides,key,financial,ratios,for,equities,based,on,symbol,Up,to,years,of,financial,ratios,are,available,and,fields,include,earnings,per,share,return,on,equity,and,price,to,earnings,All,Barchart,OnDemand,APIs,allow,for,queries,in,JSON,XML,and,CSV,formats,Developers,can,visit,BarChart,s,site,to,request,permission,for,API,usage